Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也要去CM…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也要去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是這個時間回來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  紅莉栖也一起來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太喜歡去人多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天應該沒有那麼多人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小岡倫也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部  過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:02:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一回來你就這樣陰沉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不知道真由理一直都在為你打氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我能冷靜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在明天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算今天她沒事  明天也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經數不清這是第幾遍跟你說明了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天  真由理…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概會死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始是13日的晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後每當我取消一封D-Mail  就能延後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天跟她去CM
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有辦法救她嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會看著她最後的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望知道這條世界線上準確的截止時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後根據這個再進行時間跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒別的辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來該取消的  是叫桐生萌郁的人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  內容也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她讓過去的自己不要換手機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次必須得用她的手機來發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去找這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CM由我跟她去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是順利的話  就能在真由理…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  說不定就能解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白自己在說什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒找到萌郁的話  那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:04:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會馬上聯絡你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  什麼話都可以對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是什麼  不論何時  都可以來找我談
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你一直都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論在哪條世界線上  你都不是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  在有明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人啊  超乎想像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有收到萌郁的回信  但是找到她打工的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我調查一下那邊看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐生萌郁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  以前幹了兩三天就辭職了的臨時工就是這個名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住所？我是知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐生萌郁  自殺了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒弄錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體已經送到了千代田第三醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似沒有什麼親屬  很頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自殺？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被同夥殺了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在殺真由理之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由什麼的無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼下去的話  真由理就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳躍到萌郁死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡…岡部…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真由理…真由理她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,截止時間是19:52
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃了這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是寫著的嗎  牧瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:07:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了
