Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛時間跳躍過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不給我簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  給我回信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐生萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經按你說的去做了  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我命令吧  FB
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽不到嗎？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不會原諒她的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是牧瀨  手機呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好發D-Mail
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  真由理呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在布朗管工房  42吋電視現在開著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:45.63,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊換手機  馬上就斷貨了買不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖  趕緊啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要發送了這個  真由理就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我  把手機還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？  什麼事都沒發生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你發送了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發送了  正常啟動了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了放電現象  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運探知沒有發動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,325)\fscy80\fscx80\fsp0}Reading Steiner
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運探知沒有發動…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,325)\fscy80\fscx80\fsp0}Reading Steiner
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我  還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我  還給我  還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-Mail的效果會受收件人的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用岡部的寫法不能改變桐生萌郁的行動？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她並沒有換手機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是好好確認過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四天前我換了手機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想告訴自己不要換比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在發送之前她換成別的簡訊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說不知道D-Mail的內容了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還存有收信記錄的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就調查…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會再和你聯絡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我  還給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我  還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  究竟在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  最近的情侶啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得你發送了D-Mail的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個星期前你應該收到了一條奇怪的簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未來的自己那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把內容告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  說不出口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和IBN5100和Rounder有關的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說中了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我  簡訊究竟是什麼內容
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想要手機了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫「FB」的傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的指令都是由FB下達的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB就是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就是你們的指揮官嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能背叛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是相當忠誠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個叫FB的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於你的事情好像無所謂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將會就這樣被FB所拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有聯絡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被背叛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拋棄了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  FB才不是那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:13.51,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}收件箱\N募集Rounder\NFB\N2006:6:21
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我能說出那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB是像母親一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:20.72,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎樣的工作呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:26.18,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是提供適合當事人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擁有一種時間機器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未來發來的簡訊就是證據
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.18,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:32.10,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒工作過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有任何特長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:37.78,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:41.24,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4天後  你將在這個房間裡自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待著FB的聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人在這裡孤獨地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從FB那裡已經不會再來任何聯絡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被拋棄了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從什麼時候起就沒有聯絡了  啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得這很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會死去…就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個陰暗而又空蕩蕩的房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害了真由理的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡  一個人  被拋棄  被背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像個垃圾一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷送性命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsy80\fscx80}不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不會來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連FB也不會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了「母親」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB是女的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有見過面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想見面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見面的話一定會非常失望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來連電話都沒有打過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧你能對這種傢伙言聽計從
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:19:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給了我容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容身之地？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:17.64,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古董電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.24,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在柳林神社倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:19.64,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊回收
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓我擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在擔心我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼偷走了IBN5100的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照預定要消除D-Mail
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月31日的上午11點左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:57.63,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}別去神社那是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:00.27,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}沒有東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:19:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的桐生萌郁沒有相信D-Mail嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一  還是相信了最初的D-Mail嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用別的寫法再發一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕能讓萌郁行動的只有那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能用那傢伙的手機發簡訊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該會無條件地服從
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找FB
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於他的所在有什麼線索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:20:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不可能會告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才所說的  我殺了人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是未來的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  如果是FB的命令的話你會下手的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使知道是在被利用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣繼續依賴著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拋棄而死去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4天後  8月15日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的死被這個世界所決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.36,0:21:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那種事情我可不幹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要反抗世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會救出真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投幣式儲物櫃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「{\1c&0000E0&}大樓{\r}」前
